snippet.title: JellyFish Longplay (Vircon32) [60fps]
snippet.description:
This is a gameplay for the game JellyFish, created by The R for Vircon32 console. In this game you try to dodge as many sea creatures as you can to stay alive and beat the high score.

🌏 Vircon32 website: https://www.vircon32.com
🐦 Twitter account: https://twitter.com/vircon32
